Interface SheetConditionalFormatting

    The 'Conditional Formatting' facet of Sheet(工作表的“有条件”方面)

      • addConditionalFormatting

        int addConditionalFormatting(ConditionalFormatting cf)
        Adds a copy of a ConditionalFormatting object to the sheet

        This method could be used to copy ConditionalFormatting object from one sheet to another. For example:

         ConditionalFormatting cf = sheet.getConditionalFormattingAt(index);
 newSheet.addConditionalFormatting(cf);
        (将ConditionalHandler对象的副本添加到工作表中此方法可用于将ConditionalHandler对象从一个工作表复制到另一个工作表。例如：ConditionalDeliverCF = sheet. getConditionalDeliveringAt（index）; newSheet. addConditionalHandler（ref）;)
        Parameters:
        cf - the Conditional Formatting to clone(CF -要克隆的有条件条件的对象)
        Returns:
        index of the new Conditional Formatting object(新的条件对象的索引)

      • createConditionalFormattingRule

        ConditionalFormattingRule createConditionalFormattingRule(byte comparisonOperation,
                                                          java.lang.String formula1,
                                                          java.lang.String formula2)
        A factory method allowing to create a conditional formatting rule with a cell comparison operator

        The created conditional formatting rule compares a cell value to a formula calculated result, using the specified operator. The type of the created condition is ConditionType.CELL_VALUE_IS

        (一种工厂方法，允许使用单元格比较运算符创建条件格式规则创建的条件格式规则使用指定的运算符将单元格值与公式计算结果进行比较。创建的条件的类型为ConditionType.CELL_UTE_IS)
        Parameters:
        comparisonOperation - - MUST be a constant value from ComparisonOperator:

        • BETWEEN
        • NOT_BETWEEN
        • EQUAL
        • NOT_EQUAL
        • GT
        • LT
        • GE
        • LE

        (comparisonOperator- -必须是ComparisonOperator中的常数值：BETWEEN Not_BETWEEN EQUAL Not_EQUAL GT LT GE LE)
        formula1 - - formula for the valued, compared with the cell(公式1- -值的公式，与单元格比较)
        formula2 - - second formula (only used with ComparisonOperator.BETWEEN) and ComparisonOperator.NOT_BETWEEN operations)(formula 2- -第二个公式（仅与ComparisonOperator.BETWEEN）和ComparisonOperator.Not_BETWEEN操作一起使用）)

      • createConditionalFormattingRule

        ConditionalFormattingRule createConditionalFormattingRule(byte comparisonOperation,
                                                          java.lang.String formula)
        Create a conditional formatting rule that compares a cell value to a formula calculated result, using an operator *

        The type of the created condition is ConditionType.CELL_VALUE_IS

        (使用运算符创建条件格式规则，将单元格值与公式计算结果进行比较 * 创建的条件的类型为ConditionType.CELL_UTE_IS)
        Parameters:
        comparisonOperation - MUST be a constant value from ComparisonOperator except BETWEEN and NOT_BETWEEN(comparisonOperator-必须是ComparisonOperator中的常数值，BETWEEN和NOT_BETWEEN除外)
        formula - the formula to determine if the conditional formatting is applied(公式-用于确定是否应用条件格式的公式)

      • createConditionalFormattingRule

        ConditionalFormattingRule createConditionalFormattingRule(java.lang.String formula)
        Create a conditional formatting rule based on a Boolean formula. When the formula result is true, the cell is highlighted.

        The type of the created format condition is ConditionType.FORMULA

        (基于布尔公式创建条件格式规则。当公式结果为真时，单元格将突出显示。创建的格式条件的类型为ConditionType.FORMULA)
        Parameters:
        formula - the formula to evaluate. MUST be a Boolean function.(公式-要评估的公式。必须是布尔函数。)

      • createConditionalFormattingRule

        ConditionalFormattingRule createConditionalFormattingRule(ExtendedColor color)
        Create a Databar conditional formatting rule.

        The thresholds and colour for it will be created, but will be empty and require configuring with ConditionalFormattingRule.getDataBarFormatting() then DataBarFormatting.getMinThreshold() and DataBarFormatting.getMaxThreshold()

        (创建Databar条件格式规则。将创建它的阈值和颜色，但将为空，并且需要使用ConditionalDeliveringRule. getDataBarrier（）、DataBarrier. getMinThield（）和DataBarrier. getMaxThield（）进行配置)

      • createConditionalFormattingRule

        ConditionalFormattingRule createConditionalFormattingRule(IconMultiStateFormatting.IconSet iconSet)
        Create an Icon Set / Multi-State conditional formatting rule.

        The thresholds for it will be created, but will be empty and require configuring with ConditionalFormattingRule.getMultiStateFormatting() then IconMultiStateFormatting.getThresholds()

        (创建图标集/多状态条件格式规则。将创建它的阈值，但将为空，需要使用ConditionalJourningRule. getMultiStateDeliveres（）配置，然后使用IconMultiStateDeliveres. getDeliveres（）)

      • createConditionalFormattingColorScaleRule

        ConditionalFormattingRule createConditionalFormattingColorScaleRule()
        Create a Color Scale / Color Gradient conditional formatting rule.

        The thresholds and colours for it will be created, but will be empty and require configuring with ConditionalFormattingRule.getColorScaleFormatting() then ColorScaleFormatting.getThresholds() and ColorScaleFormatting.getColors()

        (创建色标/渐变色条件格式规则。将创建它的阈值和颜色，但将为空，并且需要使用ConditionalJourningRule. getColorScaleup（）、ColorScaleup. getDocs（）和ColorScaleup.getColors（）进行配置)

      • getConditionalFormattingAt

        ConditionalFormatting getConditionalFormattingAt(int index)
        Gets Conditional Formatting object at a particular index(获取特定索引处的条件别名对象)
        Parameters:
        index - 0-based index of the Conditional Formatting object to fetch(要获取的条件别名对象的基于index - 0的索引)
        Returns:
        Conditional Formatting object or null if not found(条件别名对象，如果找不到，则为空)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if the index is outside of the allowable range (0 ... numberOfFormats-1)(java.lang. IllegalArgument例外-如果索引超出允许范围（0.人数Oftons-1）)
